Signed-off-by: Kalle Valo <kvalo@codeaurora.org>
Link: https://lore.kernel.org/r/iwlwifi.20200417100405.f5f4c4193ec1.Id5feebc9b4318041913a9c89fc1378bb5454292c@changeid
